                feature2Desc: "Get live updates on departure times and seat availability so you never miss your bus.",
                feature3Title: "Secure Payments",
                feature3Desc: "Pay easily and securely with mobile payment solutions.",
                whoWeAreTitle: "Who We Are",
                whoWeAreDesc: "GSOB Transit was built by a dynamic Rwandan student teamâ€”frontend by Mucyo Jonathan, backend by Bonheur Intwaliâ€”to streamline student travel. Our mission is simple: empower learners to explore safely, affordably, and effortlessly.",
                footerTitle: "GSOB Transit",
